{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Analysis + fix in PR #51 (auto-merge enabled). WHICH CRITERIA should have caught it: E5 (testing, runs on story+task) and E6 (ac-text-quality, task-only) were best-positioned. E5 missed because 'thin-but-present coverage = PASS' had no concept of a mock that bypasses the new path; E6 missed because it treated the offline proving command as sufficient AND is routed task-only (never ran on the B5 STORY — so E5 is the actual catch for story cutovers). FIX (strengthen E5+E6 per direction): E5 gains PROXY-VALIDATION anti-pattern (defaulted path validated only via offline mock = MAJOR); E6 gains PROVING-COMMAND-EXERCISES-THE-CHANGE (cutover needs a live e2e AC; green offline + signed verdict necessary-but-not-sufficient); matching checklist bullets render into the finder prompt; B5-shaped eval recall cases + anti-over-fire good pair + offline presence test; docs/plan-review-gate.md cutover-DoD section; coaching via existing Pass-4 moves 7/9. Left E6 routing task-only to avoid broad over-fire (noted as possible follow-up). No index drift; 256 tests + eval-discipline pass. Will close on merge."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782529124282747001,"uuid":"a7b3e617-ab3d-4bd5-b209-cca001504320"}